        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer832200250" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8391303604436640163">Unlike the first Chronicles, this is really one long story. Covenant is an actual person in these books, perhaps because of his position relative to Linden Avery. Donaldson still reads much like an anime show sounds, though; so much happens at top emotional pitch.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


